```

Execute the application with debugging, and start toggling the RightToLeft value in the combo box until the exception occurs.

![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/72593e26-929e-4dfb-b3ee-7a49f36b3bbf)

The exception happens during processing a `WM_COMMAND` for the native child window of the `ComboBox` by `DefWndProc`.

